        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer550506055" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13555074582495996592">I really enjoyed <i>Manuscript Found in Accra</i>. This is a book that is full of uplifting, timeless wisdom. It is the type of book that can be read quickly, but it is really best read and processed slowly and revisited from time to time. I am sure that I will re-read it again in the future, so it is a welcome addition to my library. <br/><br/>I received a free copy of this book through the Goodreads First Reads program.</span>

          </span>
